lead_paragraph: South Africa skipper Faf du Plessis described Kagiso Rabada's performance as "phenomenal" after the young paceman helped turn a parlous situation on day two of the first test against Australia into a thumping 177-run victory on Monday.

headline.print_headline: 'Phenomenal' Rabada Fires South Africa to Victory
headline.main: 'Phenomenal' Rabada Fires South Africa to Victory
